{
  "texts": [
    "If symbolic terms encapsulate some aspects of linguistic structure, we anticipate statistical learning-based models will likewise embed these structures 31, 32.",
    "Indeed 8, [57] [58] [59] [60], succeeded in extracting linguistic information from contextual embeddings.",
    "However, it is important to note that although large language models may capture soft rule-like statistical regularities, this does not transform them into rule-based symbolic systems.",
    "Deep language models rely on statistical rather than symbolic foundations for linguistic representations.",
    "By analyzing language statistics, these models embed language structure into a continuous space."
  ]
}